data.description: OVERSIZED CORNER LOT! 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2-car garage pool home in central Port Charlotte and includes 2 bonus rooms for additional living space or den/office. Metal roof, new hurricane doors and windows, new hot water heater plus new ac in 2017. Flood insurance is transferrable. Open floor plan features luxury vinyl flooring, spacious living room, dining room and kitchen with access to lanai and pool, master suite with sliders, walk-in closet and private bath with dual sinks and walk-in shower. Plenty of space with 2 guest bedrooms and 2 bonus rooms with one off garage. Outdoor entertaining area features covered lanai and heated screened 14’x28’ pool overlooking fenced in area for furry friends to roam. Lots of privacy, screened front entry, child safety fence for pool and two outdoor sheds for extra storage. Great location just a short drive to Port Charlotte Beach Park, new Sunseeker Resort, Punta Gorda airport and close to Murdock restaurant and shopping district, schools, golf and downtown historic Punta Gorda with community events and entertainment plus easy access to SWFL gulf beaches. Don’t miss this opportunity! Schedule your private showing today!
